    "user_title": "Create animated GIFs for Slack",
    "value_statement": "Create animated GIFs that meet Slack size limits. Build animations with composable primitives like shake, bounce, spin, pulse, fade, zoom, and explode. Validates file size and dimensions for emoji and message GIFs.",
    "seo_keywords": [
      "slack gif creator",
