        "prompt": "Create a crossfade morph animation between two emojis. Use ease_in_out easing. Validate the result meets Slack emoji size requirements."
      },
      {
        "title": "Complex composition",
        "scenario": "Combine multiple animation effects",
        "prompt": "Create a composite animation that combines move, shake, and impact flash effects. Include text overlay with outline. Optimize for Slack message GIF."
      }
